edb8a288-ed83-41b5-8dfc-ec400cbfbd3d.title: Donnie
edb8a288-ed83-41b5-8dfc-ec400cbfbd3d.text: Hello there, can I help you?

options.text: Are there any quests I can do here?
Where can I get a haircut like yours?

63cd4a01-6582-45de-9926-9d4cdf94bcba.title: Donnie
63cd4a01-6582-45de-9926-9d4cdf94bcba.text: This is the town of Lumbridge my friend.

options.text: Are there any quests I can do here?
Where can I get a haircut like yours?

1aeef7a9-decb-4b33-bdf3-303d5b7e1a2f.title: Donnie
1aeef7a9-decb-4b33-bdf3-303d5b7e1a2f.text: Aye, not too bad thank you. Lovely weather in Gielinor this fine day.

dd013595-33a0-49a5-9f4c-26bca58f4b35.title: Donnie
dd013595-33a0-49a5-9f4c-26bca58f4b35.text:
The state or condition of the atmosphere at a time and
place, with respect to variables such as temperature,
moisture, wind velocity, and barometric pressure.

d2112ca4-abb4-4bc7-8576-afd513f66b74.title: Donnie
d2112ca4-abb4-4bc7-8576-afd513f66b74.text: Not just a pretty face eh? Ha ha ha.

c111a74d-bafb-4ce3-8e23-bea6f47e1e1b.title: <player>
c111a74d-bafb-4ce3-8e23-bea6f47e1e1b.text: Do you know of any quests I can do?

53279dff-0a99-447e-b219-0018401452c6.title: Donnie
53279dff-0a99-447e-b219-0018401452c6.text: What kind of quest are you looking for?

f238d4d5-3c39-417c-bca7-af1a4924f8c1.title: <player>
f238d4d5-3c39-417c-bca7-af1a4924f8c1.text: Where can I get a haircut like yours?

4fead3a4-4845-4664-8fc2-0a1ebb65abf2.title: Donnie
4fead3a4-4845-4664-8fc2-0a1ebb65abf2.text: Yes, it does look like you need a hairdresser.

ba080af9-46e6-47d6-bdb5-d58b19660546.title: Donnie
ba080af9-46e6-47d6-bdb5-d58b19660546.text:
No problem. The hairdresser in Falador will probably be
able to sort you out.

dce5b165-d671-4d37-8ee4-c33db94d4ac2.title: Donnie
dce5b165-d671-4d37-8ee4-c33db94d4ac2.text:
The Lumbridge general store sells useful maps if you
don't know the way.

options.text: Are there any quests I can do here?

94a2bb1d-1828-4559-a2ab-0fb1e15154ca.title: Donnie
94a2bb1d-1828-4559-a2ab-0fb1e15154ca.text: I assume the sky is up..

02185b3d-ddd2-4d7d-a4f6-c5674623d81c.title: Donnie
02185b3d-ddd2-4d7d-a4f6-c5674623d81c.text: Yea, unfortunately I don't seem to be able to look up.

options.text: Do you have anything of value which I can have?
Are there any quests I can do here?

3e3e3bb2-a7fd-4ba3-aad2-d2e8e0592fe0.title: Donnie
3e3e3bb2-a7fd-4ba3-aad2-d2e8e0592fe0.text: It's not a stick! I'll have you know it's a very powerful staff!

c6b2da56-cfa7-4ae8-a68a-1ca03404d594.title: <player>
c6b2da56-cfa7-4ae8-a68a-1ca03404d594.text: Really? Show me what it can do!

56c23ba9-ee28-4bc4-8947-af2648112496.title: Donnie
56c23ba9-ee28-4bc4-8947-af2648112496.text: Um..It's a bit low on power at the moment..

ae3441cc-3ac8-42fe-bbb9-6c100c5731ba.title: Donnie
ae3441cc-3ac8-42fe-bbb9-6c100c5731ba.text:
...Ok it's a stick.. But only while I save up for a staff.
Zaff in Varrock square sells them in his shop.

options.text: Are there any quests I can do here?

3ecfbf58-cae5-4347-a255-b69228a74598.title: <player>
3ecfbf58-cae5-4347-a255-b69228a74598.text: No you're right. I have nothing to back that up.

options.text: I fancy a bit of a fight, anything dangerous?
Something easy please, I'm new here.
I'm a thinker rather then a fighter, anything skill oriented?
I want to do all kinds of things, do you know of anything like that?

75d96f0f-5bf6-4186-80e7-6cd23010ad4b.title: <player>
75d96f0f-5bf6-4186-80e7-6cd23010ad4b.text: I fancy a bit of a fight, anything dangerous?

539957e1-914a-4cef-b1b6-c0db3c304caf.title: Donnie
539957e1-914a-4cef-b1b6-c0db3c304caf.text: Hmm... dangerous you say? What sort of creatures are you looking to fight?

options.text: Small.. something small would be good.

23670124-dc2e-4362-a45b-189f6a46d47d.title: Donnie
23670124-dc2e-4362-a45b-189f6a46d47d.text: You are a brave soul indeed.

e3e40f7b-e279-4c83-86bc-a1d68c6bf8ab.title: Donnie
e3e40f7b-e279-4c83-86bc-a1d68c6bf8ab.text:
Now that you mention it, I heard a rumour about a
gypsy in Varrock who is rambling about some kind of a
greater evil.. sounds demon-line if you ask me.

89b5eda5-6be7-492e-98cc-7aec57527e2a.title: Donnie
89b5eda5-6be7-492e-98cc-7aec57527e2a.text: Perhaps you could check it out if you are as brave as you say?

4bd413d9-8081-4bd4-bfa3-77a4cc9879d5.title: <player>
4bd413d9-8081-4bd4-bfa3-77a4cc9879d5.text: Thanks for the tip, perhaps I will.

49f005a0-e31f-4561-8102-86b8eec8fb9c.title: Donnie
49f005a0-e31f-4561-8102-86b8eec8fb9c.text:
Ha ha. I personally don't believe in such things.
However, there is a man in Draynor Village who has
been scaring the village folk with stories of vampyres.

08789e81-1ebd-4585-924c-033f808cd9c5.title: Donnie
08789e81-1ebd-4585-924c-033f808cd9c5.text:
He's named Morgan and can be found in one of the
village houses. Perhaps you could see what the matter
is?

8fe34ae3-b802-433f-9bac-4c00642ca280.title: <player>
8fe34ae3-b802-433f-9bac-4c00642ca280.text: Small.. something small would be good.

7cb91f83-b6c4-482f-b8d8-42043178a5ed.title: Donnie
7cb91f83-b6c4-482f-b8d8-42043178a5ed.text: Small? Small isn't really that dangerous though is it?

0dae00a6-8ed6-4b45-ad5d-965276b9a63d.title: <player>
0dae00a6-8ed6-4b45-ad5d-965276b9a63d.text:
Yes it can be! There could be anything from an evil
chicken to a poisonous spider. They attack in numbers
you know!

f0bbb846-8e25-4389-ae17-2e1ff5c3502c.title: <player>
f0bbb846-8e25-4389-ae17-2e1ff5c3502c.text:
Yes ok, point taken. Speaking of small monsters, I hear
old Wizard Mizgog in the wizards' tower has just had
all his beads taken by a gang of mischievous imps.

8f44ac16-440f-45e2-b3d2-849bb33766af.title: <player>
8f44ac16-440f-45e2-b3d2-849bb33766af.text: sounds like it could be a quest for  you?

be501a57-7011-453e-85a5-9aef7ae10c4b.title: <player>
be501a57-7011-453e-85a5-9aef7ae10c4b.text: Something easy please, I'm new here.

fe09b01e-6c45-4110-956b-59451139759a.title: Donnie
fe09b01e-6c45-4110-956b-59451139759a.text: I can tell you about plenty of small easy taks.

dc075697-06a7-43b4-a11a-5df4443a31ea.title: Donnie
dc075697-06a7-43b4-a11a-5df4443a31ea.text:
The  Lumbridge cook has been having problems, the
Duke is confused over some strange rocks and on top
of all that, poor lad Romeo in Varrock has girlfriend
problems.

c57c292e-a429-48e9-a7a9-30b2e838bdea.title: <player>
c57c292e-a429-48e9-a7a9-30b2e838bdea.text: Tell me about Fred the farmer please.

32b76853-f029-4fe3-86fd-8a20ab64733b.title: Donnie
32b76853-f029-4fe3-86fd-8a20ab64733b.text:
You can find Fred next to the field of sheep in
Lumbridge. Perhaps you should go and speak with him.

0cf925f5-db03-4580-a26a-04fd3449a997.title: <player>
0cf925f5-db03-4580-a26a-04fd3449a997.text: Tell me about Doric the dwarf.

e7a5c367-d639-4904-9880-0b9f9a1329a0.title: Donnie
e7a5c367-d639-4904-9880-0b9f9a1329a0.text:
Doric the dwarf is located north of Falador. He might
be able to help you with smithing. You should speak to
him. He may let you use his anvils.

822f9180-a4e7-40fb-ae86-974900565b8c.title: <player>
822f9180-a4e7-40fb-ae86-974900565b8c.text: I'm a thinker rather then a fighter, anything skill oriented?

3e321c01-fd20-4769-8edb-6d114472086d.title: Donnie
3e321c01-fd20-4769-8edb-6d114472086d.text:
Skills play a big part when you want to progress in
knowledge throught Gielinor. I know of a few skill-
related quests that can get you started.

e0462e10-2821-49e2-ab00-25386155ab47.title: Donnie
e0462e10-2821-49e2-ab00-25386155ab47.text:
You may be able to help out Fred the farmer who is in
need of someones crafting expertise.

ff843d1a-b62e-4c38-9a61-f65db8478824.title: Donnie
ff843d1a-b62e-4c38-9a61-f65db8478824.text: Or, there's always Doric the dwarf who needs an errand running for him?

851f89a2-a1ec-4e2a-8306-ec8febdf3a86.title: <player>
851f89a2-a1ec-4e2a-8306-ec8febdf3a86.text: Tell me about the Lumbridge cook.

0294cf15-08ab-4484-8a3d-30b4372169b9.title: Donnie
0294cf15-08ab-4484-8a3d-30b4372169b9.text:
It's funny really, the cook would forget his head if it
wasn't screws on. This time he forgot to get
ingredients for the Duke's birthday cake.

9c9cd761-c1e4-4328-8e1a-9ce63467b209.title: Donnie
9c9cd761-c1e4-4328-8e1a-9ce63467b209.text:
Perhaps you could help him? You will probably find him
in the Lumbridge Castle kitchen.

aeb2f4f7-71bb-4f3f-b9cd-02ba7860d888.title: <player>
aeb2f4f7-71bb-4f3f-b9cd-02ba7860d888.text: Thank you. I shall go speak with him.

38215487-7244-4500-b664-d6374e8f16b0.title: <player>
38215487-7244-4500-b664-d6374e8f16b0.text: Tell me about the Duke's strange rocks.

9eb31706-6694-4547-8729-f1e4e826c37d.title: Donnie
9eb31706-6694-4547-8729-f1e4e826c37d.text:
Well the Duke of Lumbridge has found a strange stone
that no one seems to understand. Perhaps you could
help him? You can probably find him upstairs in
Lumbridge Castle.

838ac614-308e-43f3-bd22-2dd9dc26a585.title: <player>
838ac614-308e-43f3-bd22-2dd9dc26a585.text: Sounds mysterious. I may just do that. Thanks.

51b7eaef-e142-4059-bd6e-a624d7696c45.title: <player>
51b7eaef-e142-4059-bd6e-a624d7696c45.text: Tell me about Romeo and his girlfriend please.

886108bf-825b-408b-9520-da85e9f9135d.title: Donnie
886108bf-825b-408b-9520-da85e9f9135d.text:
Romeo in Varrock needs help with finding his beloved
Juliet, you may be able to help him out.

90741b24-5da8-452c-9780-8161b47c9ac9.title: Donnie
90741b24-5da8-452c-9780-8161b47c9ac9.text:
Unless of course you manage to find Juliet first in
which case she has probably lost Romeo.

e2d78545-db1a-481a-bbc3-8297c0881713.title: <player>
e2d78545-db1a-481a-bbc3-8297c0881713.text: Right, ok. Romeo is in Varrock?

b788feae-0f3f-40a2-86b9-83776d0f3b0a.title: Donnie
b788feae-0f3f-40a2-86b9-83776d0f3b0a.text:
Yes you can't miss him, he's wandering aimlessly in the
square.

3d72b3b1-696e-433e-a2df-9bcb7571d5d7.title: <player>
3d72b3b1-696e-433e-a2df-9bcb7571d5d7.text: I want to do all kinds of things, do you know of anyhting like that?

93a45e31-bc3a-445c-9037-cdf5f75e47d5.title: Donnie
93a45e31-bc3a-445c-9037-cdf5f75e47d5.text:
Of course I do. Gielinor is a huge place you know, now
let me think...

38b553af-5238-4c51-938f-af57a1fbdc2b.title: Donnie
38b553af-5238-4c51-938f-af57a1fbdc2b.text:
Hetty the witch in Rimmington might be able to offer
help in the ways of magical abilities..

494223a8-ca6b-46b7-8c92-aaffd8ea0e20.title: Donnie
494223a8-ca6b-46b7-8c92-aaffd8ea0e20.text:
Also, pirates are currently docked in Port Sarim,
Where pirates are, treasure is never far away...

b960a01e-3804-4fa0-87e8-d1f64bfb325a.title: Donnie
b960a01e-3804-4fa0-87e8-d1f64bfb325a.text:
Or you could go help out Ernest who got lost in
Draynor Manor, spooky place that.

d9fb3e84-b3a5-4858-928b-fc1cacc004fa.title: <player>
d9fb3e84-b3a5-4858-928b-fc1cacc004fa.text: Tell me about Hetty the witch.

15694145-5fd4-4d06-b205-91a6b0a7a6a7.title: Donnie
15694145-5fd4-4d06-b205-91a6b0a7a6a7.text:
Hetty the witch can be found in Rimmington, south of
Falador. She's currently working on some new potions.
Perhaps you could give her a hand? She might be able
to offer help with your magical abilities.

16f756f6-76c7-4a55-b2c5-7c2f3eb2144e.title: <player>
16f756f6-76c7-4a55-b2c5-7c2f3eb2144e.text: Ok thanks, let's hope she doesn't turn me into a potato or something..

a8bbcb76-8301-4608-a38c-2882934b9bfe.title: Donnie
a8bbcb76-8301-4608-a38c-2882934b9bfe.text:
Red Beard Frank in Port Sarim's bar, the Rusty
Anchor, might be able to tell you about the rumoured
treasure that is buries somewhere in Gielinor.

613ff3ae-dbe0-4e20-bf90-a7860612a361.title: <player>
613ff3ae-dbe0-4e20-bf90-a7860612a361.text:
Sounds adventurous, I may have to check that out.
Thank you.

fcaa58fd-b5ac-436c-b049-ec31744fcd01.title: Donnie
fcaa58fd-b5ac-436c-b049-ec31744fcd01.text:
The best place to start would be at the gate to
Draynor Manor. There you will find Veronica who will
be able to tell you more.

abbf5506-d270-4407-a280-68197be6f910.title: Donnie
abbf5506-d270-4407-a280-68197be6f910.text: I suggest you tread carefully in the place; it's haunted.

a6e48f25-f85f-4dd4-96fb-eb572aa3850a.title: <player>
a6e48f25-f85f-4dd4-96fb-eb572aa3850a.text:
Sounds like fun. I've never been to a Haunted Manor
before.
